%h1 Registre des modifications

- @activities_by_date.each do |date, activities|
  - if activities.any?
    %h2= l(date.to_date)

    - activities.each do |activity|
      = div_for activity, class: 'activity' do
        = render_activity activity

  %hr

.row
  .col-sm-6= paginate @activities, theme: 'twitter-bootstrap'
  .col-sm-6= link_to 'Vider le registre', empty_activity_path, method: :delete, class: 'btn btn-danger btn-lg', data: {confirm: 'Etes-vous s√ªr ?'} if current_user.admin?
